        "custom_liquid": "<div class=\"policy-page\">\n  <h1>Returns, Exchanges & Refunds Policy</h1>\n\n  <p>We offer a 7-day return and exchange policy. If more than 7 days have passed since your order was delivered, we will not be able to offer a return, exchange, or refund.</p>\n\n  <h2>At a Glance</h2>\n  <ul>\n    <li>Returns and exchanges can be requested within 7 days of delivery.</li>\n    <li>Products must be unused and returned in original packaging.</li>\n    <li>Exchanges are subject to stock availability.</li>\n    <li>Refunds are applicable only for wrong, damaged, or defective products after verification.</li>\n    <li>For damaged or incorrect items, an unboxing video is mandatory.</li>\n  </ul>\n\n  <h2>Eligibility for Returns & Exchanges</h2>\n  <p>To be eligible, the product must be unused, unworn, unwashed, and returned with all original packaging, tags, invoice, and accessories.</p>\n\n  <h2>Non-Eligible Requests</h2>\n  <ul>\n    <li>Request raised after 7 days of delivery.</li>\n    <li>Product is worn, used, washed, damaged, or altered.</li>\n    <li>Original box, tags, invoice, or packaging is missing.</li>\n    <li>Product fails quality inspection.</li>\n    <li>Damage claim without a proper unboxing video.</li>\n  </ul>\n\n  <h2>Refund Eligibility</h2>\n  <p>Refunds will be provided only if the wrong product is delivered or the product is received damaged/defective. Refunds are processed after inspection and approval by our team.</p>\n\n  <h2>Refund Processing</h2>\n  <p>Approved refunds will be processed within 5–7 working days after the returned product is received and verified.</p>\n\n  <h2>Damaged, Defective or Incorrect Products</h2>\n  <p>If you receive a damaged, defective, or incorrect product, contact us immediately with:</p>\n  <ul>\n    <li>Complete unboxing video before opening the package.</li>\n    <li>Clear photo/video of the issue.</li>\n    <li>Order ID and registered mobile number/email.</li>\n  </ul>\n\n  <h2>Start a Return or Exchange</h2>\n  <p>To request a return or exchange, please contact our support team with your order details.</p>\n\n  <a href=\"/pages/contact\" class=\"policy-btn\">Contact Support</a>\n</div>\n\n<style>\n.policy-page{\n  max-width:900px;\n  margin:50px auto;\n  padding:30px 20px;\n  font-family:inherit;\n  color:#111;\n  line-height:1.7;\n}\n\n.policy-page h1{\n  font-size:42px;\n  margin-bottom:25px;\n  text-align:left;\n}\n\n.policy-page h2{\n  font-size:24px;\n  margin-top:35px;\n  margin-bottom:12px;\n}\n\n.policy-page p,\n.policy-page li{\n  font-size:16px;\n}\n\n.policy-page ul{\n  padding-left:22px;\n}\n\n.policy-btn{\n  display:inline-block;\n  margin-top:25px;\n  padding:14px 28px;\n  background:#111;\n  color:#fff;\n  text-decoration:none;\n  border-radius:4px;\n  font-weight:600;\n}\n\n.policy-btn:hover{\n  background:#333;\n}\n\n@media(max-width:768px){\n  .policy-page h1{\n    font-size:32px;\n  }\n}\n</style>",
